Regular Season Structure
Total Games: 82 per team. 
Division Play: 4 games against each of the 4 other teams in their division (16 games). 
Conference Play:
4 games against 6 out-of-division conference teams (24 games). 
3 games against the remaining 4 conference teams (12 games), determined by a 5-year rotation. 
Inter-Conference Play: 2 games against each of the 15 teams in the opposing conference (30 games). 


